{"tid":1012162,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解過左兩個幾月都仲係咁痛","createTime":"2019-02-07T11:01:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T06:49:13.000Z","uid":133823,"like":29,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d54865011337cd6e91816e74c853027a20183c6a","tid":1012162,"uid":133823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T11:01:38.000Z","msg":"點解每當我以為自己overcome左<br />\n所有感覺就即刻返晒黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好盡力咁去fill up自己時間表<br />\n不斷搵野去做去睇去充實自己<br />\n但點解我做所有野都會諗起你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔想當你係朋友<br />\n唔想知你同我散左之後同其他人有幾開心<br />\n唔想再係所有人面前扮堅強<br />\n唔想有識過你呀<br />\n<br />\n睇完500 days of summer<br />\n我明白我唔係改變到你既the one<br />\n我地唔係meant to be together <br />\n我明個道理<br />\n但我真係好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c680f2ed22d8ce0722ca2630f8578141bb87cd92","tid":1012162,"uid":118989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T11:06:26.000Z","msg":"砍掉重練"},{"pid":"7c19cf0fab21c0b82b85a2ab0c416a760c1adf5a","tid":1012162,"uid":140798,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T11:12:40.000Z","msg":"兩個幾月咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afa0b2e6a575691e953053e0f007036e3898aecc","tid":1012162,"uid":133823,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7c19cf0fab21c0b82b85a2ab0c416a760c1adf5a","tid":1012162,"uid":140798,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T11:12:40.000Z","msg":"兩個幾月咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T11:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c9MmhzG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc9MmhzG.png&h=e91a5ae9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"beedfa75b79c4eaf045bfd10129f8f78c740bafd","tid":1012162,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T1